hadiths[150]{hadithnumber,text}:
1030,Hazrat Alqama aur Aswad sey marwi hai ke hum dono Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar mein unkey sath they to unhoney farmaya : kya ye log namaz padh chukey hain? hamney kaha : ji haan. to unhoney hum dono ko baghair Azan aur iqaamat key namaz padhaai aur hamarey darmiyan khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : jab tum teen aadmi ho to isi tarah kya karo aur jab tum teen sey ziyada ho to phir tum mein sey eik (Imam aagey khada ho kar) jamaat kiraey aur (rukoo mein) apney bazu raanon par bicha kar (dono haath eik doosrey mein phansa kar ghutnon key darmiyan) rakh ley. mujhey aisey mehsus hota hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki ungliyon ko eik dusri mein phansi hui dekh raha hun.
1031,Hazrat Aswad aur Alqama sey riwayat hai ke hamney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath unkey ghar mein namaz padhi. aap hamarey darmiyan khadey huye. (rukoo mein) hamney apney haath apney ghutnon par rakh liye. unhoney hamarey haathon ko ghutnon sey hata diya aur eik haath ki ungliyon ko doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein phansa diya. aur (raanon key darmiyan rakhwaya) phir farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai.
1032,"Hazrat Alqama sey manqul hai, Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaz sikhlai. phir Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur « Allahu-akbar » kaha. jab rukoo karney ka irada kya to apney haathon ki ungliyon ko eik dusrey mein phansa kar haathon ko ghutnon key darmiyan rakh liya. ye baat Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ko pahunchi to unhoney farmaya, merey bhai (Ibne-Masood) ney sach kaha magar hum ye kaam pehley kya kartey they, phir (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey) hamen ghutney pakadney ka hukm diya gaya."
1033,"Musab bin Saad sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : mainey apney walid key pehlu mein namaz padhi aur mainey apney haath apney ghutnon key darmiyan rakh liye to walid mohtaram ney mujh sey kaha : apney haath apney ghutnon par rakho. mainey eik dafa phir isi tarah kya to unhoney merey haath par maara aur farmaya : yaqinan hamen is kaam sey roka gaya hai, aur hamen hukm diya gaya hai ke hum haath ghutnon par rakhen."
1034,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey rukoo mein tatbiq ki to merey walid mohtaram ney farmaya : ye kaam hum pehley kya kartey they, phir hamen ghutnon key ooper haath rakhney key liye kaha gaya."
1035,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tumharey liye ghutnon ko pakadney ka tariqa raaij kya gaya hai, lihaza ghutnon ko pakda karo."
1036,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain (rukoo mein) ghutnon ko pakadna sunnat hai.
1037,Hazrat Salim bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey aur un sey guzarish ki ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz bayan kijiye. aap hamarey aagey khadey ho gaey aur Allahu-akbar kaha. jab aap ney rukoo kya to apni hatheliyan apney ghutnon par rakhin aur ungliyan us sey nichey rakhen aur apni kohniyon ko pehluon sey door rakha yahan tak ke aap ka har uzu sidha aur durust ho gaya. phir « Samiallahu liman hamida » kaha aur khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke aap ka har uzu sidha aur durust ho gaya.
1038,Hazrat Salim sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aqba bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya main tumharey samney is tarah namaz na padhun jis tarah mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko padhtey dekha hai? hamney kaha : kyon nahin! aap khadey huye. jab rukoo kya to apni hatheliyan apney ghutnon par rakhin aur apni ungliyon ko ghutnon sey nichey rakha aur apni baghlon ko khola (baazuon ko pehlu sey door rakha) yahan tak ke aap ka har uzu sidha aur durust ho gaya ( apni jagah par jam gaya) phir aap ney apna sar uthaya aur khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke aap ka har uzu sidha ho gaya. phir aap ney sajda kya aur apni baghlon ko khola (baazuon ko pehlu sey door rakha ) yahan tak ke aap ka har uzu (apni jagah par) thehar gaya. phir bethey yahan tak ke aap ka har uzu (apni jagah par) thehar gaya. phir sajda kya yahan tak ke har uzu (apni jagah par) thehar gaya. phir aap ney chaaron rakaat mein isi tarah kya. phir farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah namaz padhtey dekha hai aur aap hamen isi tarah namaz padhatey they.
1039,"Hazrat Salim Baraad sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya main tumhein na dikhaaun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kaisey namaz padhtey they? hamney kaha : han, zarur. aap khadey huye aur (Allahu-Akbar) kaha. phir jab rukoo kiya to apni baghlon ko khub khola yahan tak ke jab aap ka har uzu ( iapni jagah par) jam gaya to aap ney apna sar uthaya. phir chaaron rakaat isi tarah padhein aur farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah namaz padhtey dekha hai."
1040,Hazrat abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo farmatey to miyaana rawi ikhtiyar farmatey yani na to apna sar bahut nichey jhukaatey aur na usey ooper uthatey (balke pusht key barabar rakhtey). aur aap apney dono haath apney dono ghutnon par rakhtey.
1041,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney « Qassi» aur reshmi kapdey aur soney ki anguthi pehanney sey roka hai aur us baat sey bhi ke main rukoo ki haalat mein Quran Majeed padhun.
1042,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney soney ki anguthi pehanney, rukoo mein qirat Quran kerney, Qassi aur «Maasfar» (zafrani zard rang ka kapda) pehanney sey mana kya hai."
1043,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey … … … mein nahin kehta ke tumhein … … … soney ki anguthi, Qassi kapdey, khalis aur intehai surkh aur zaafrani zard rang key kapdey pehanney aur rukoo mein Quran Majeed padhney sey mana farmaya hai."
1044,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Qassi aur Maasfar (Zaafrani zard rang ka) kapda aur soney ki anguthi pehanney aur rukoo mein Quran Majeed padhney sey mana farmaya hai.
1045,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Qassi, zaafrani zard rang key kapdey aur soney ki anguthi pehanney aur rukoo mein Quran Majeed padhney sey mana farmaya hai."
1046,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( darwazey ka) parda hataya jab ke log Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechey safein bandhey huye they. aap ney farmaya : aey logo! nabuwat sey makhsus khush-khabri deney wali chizon mein sey ab nek aur sachchey khuwab hi reh gaey hain jo koi musalman khud dekh ley ya uskey liye kisi aur ko nazar aaye. phir farmaya : khabardar! mujhey rukoo ya sajdey ki haalat mein Quran Majeed padhney sey roka gaya hai, chunanche rukoo mein rab taala ki azmat bayan karo aur sajdey mein dua maangney ki koshish karo (pura zor laga do kyonkey ) sajdey mein dua qubuliyat key ziyada laaiq hai."
1047,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi. aap ney rukoo farmaya to apney rukoo mein (Subhan rabbiyal azeem ) pak hai mera azmaton wala rab. aur sajdey mein (subhan rabbiyal-aala) pak hai mera buland o baala rab. padha.
1048,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo aur sajdey mein aksar ye dua padha kartey they : سبحانک ربنا و بحمدک اللھم اغفرلی aey hamarey rab! to har qism key naqaayis o uyub sey pak hai aur har qism ki taarifon ka mustahiq hai. aey Allah mujhey maaf farma dey.
1049,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) rukoo mein سبوح قدوس رب الملائکۃ و الروح bahut pak hai, balatar hai farishton aur rooh (Jibril ameen) ka rab. padha kartey they."
1050,Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik raat namaz mein khada huwa. jab aap ney rukoo farmaya to Sura Baqra key b-qadr rukoo mein thehrey rahey aur padhtey rahey : سبحان ذی الجبروت والملکوت والکبریاء والعظمۃ pak hai azimushshan ghalbey aur badi badshahat wala aur be inteha buzurgi (badai) aur azmat wala rab.
1051,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo farmatey to yun padhtey : اللھم ! لک رکعت … … … و عصبی aey Allah ! main terey samney jhuka, apney aap ko terey supurd kya aur tujh par eman laya, merey kaan, aankhen, haddiyan, maghz aur patthey sab terey samney ijz o niaz zahir kartey hain."
1052,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo farmatey to yun kehtey :  اللھم ! لک رکعت … … … رب العلمین aey Allah ! main terey samney jhuka, tujh par eman laya, apney aap ko terey supurd kya aur tujhi par bharosa kya. to mera rab hai. merey kanon, aakhon, khoon, gosht, haddiyon aur putthon ney Allah azz-w-jall key samney ijz o niaz zahir kya jo tamam jahano ka paalne-wala hai."
1053,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab nafl namaz mein khadey hotey to rukoo key doran mein yun arz kartey : aey Allah ! main terey liye jhuka, tujhey maana, tera farmanbardar bana aur tujh par bharosa kya. to mera rab hai. merey kaan, aankhen, gosht, khoon, maghz aur patthey Allah rabbul-Alameen key samney aajizi aur tawaazoh kartey hain."
1054,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu), jo Badri sahabi hain, sey riwayat hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke eik aadmi masjid mein aaya aur us ney namaz padhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey dekhtey rahey jab ke usey ilm na tha. phir wo ( namaz sey) farigh huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap ko salam kya. aap ney salam ka jawab diya, phir farmaya : wapis ja, phir namaz padh. tuney namaz nahin padhi. na malum dusri ya teesri dafa us ney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap par kitab utaari ! mainey to puri koshish sey namaz padhi hai. mujhey sikhla dijiye aur batla dijiye. aap ney farmaya : jab to namaz ka irada karey to wuzu kar aur achi tarah wuzu kar. phir khada ho aur qibley ki taraf munh kar. phir « Allahu-akbar » keh. phir Quran Majeed padh. phir rukoo kar yahan tak ke itminan sey rukoo kar ley. phir sar utha yahan tak ke to sidha khada ho jaey. phir sajda kar yahan tak ke itminan sey sajda kar ley. phir sar utha yahan tak ke itminan sey beth jaey. phir sajda kar yahan tak ke itminan sey sajda kar ley. jab to (har rakat mein) ye kar lega to apni namaz ada kar lega aur jis qadr to is mein kami kerega, apni namaz mein kami kerega."
1055,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum rukoo aur sajda karo to rukoo aur sujood mukammal kya karo."
1056,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey namaz padhi to dekha ke aap jab namaz shuru farmatey ya rukoo ko jatey ya « Samiallahu liman hamida » kehtey to is tarah rafaul-yadein kartey. (Hadees key raawi) Qais ney kanon ki taraf ishara kya, yani kanon tak."
1057,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap jab rukoo farmatey ya rukoo sey sar uthatey to apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhein kanon key kinaron key barabar ley jatey."
1058,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru farmatey to apney dono haath apney kandhon key barabar uthatey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to phir isi tarah kartey aur jab (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kehtey to (ربنا لک الحمد) kehtey. aur aap sajdon key darmiyan (sajdey sey uthtey aur sajdey ko jatey waqt) rafaul-yadein nahin kartey they.
1059,Hazrat Alqama sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya main tumhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz jaisi namaz na padhaun? to unhoney namaz padhi aur eik dafa sey zayed rafaul-yadein na kiya.
1060,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru farmatey to apney kandhon key barabar haath uthatey aur jab rukoo ki takbir kehtey aur jab rukoo sey apna sar uthatey to phir unhein isi tarah uthatey aur kehtey :(Samiallahu-liman-hamida) (ربنا ولک الحمد) aur aap sajdey mein rafaul-yadein nahin kartey they.
1061,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to ( اللھم ! ربنا ولک الحمد ) kehtey.
1062,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghodey sey daeyn pehlu par gir padey to sahaba bimar pursi key liye aap ki khidmat mein hazir huye. namaz ka waqt ho gaya. jab aap ney namaz puri kar li to farmaya : Imam is liye hota hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey, lihaza jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo aur jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthaao aur jab (Samiallahu liman hamida) kahe to tum (ربنا ولک الحمد) kaho."
1063,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, farmatey hain : hum eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey namaz padh rahey they. jab aap ney rukoo sey sar uthaya to kaha (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) aap key muqtadiyon mein sey eik aadmi ney (zara buland aawaz sey) kaha : (ربنا ولک الحمد حمدا کثیرا طیبا مبارکا فیہ),''aey hamarey Rab ! terey hi liye sab tareefen hain. bahut ziyada, pakizah aur ba-barkat tareefen. jab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : kis shakhs ney abhi kuchh kalam kiya tha? padhi. us aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mainey tees sey zayed farishton ko dekha ke wo in kalimaat ki taraf eik dusrey sey sabqat kar rahey they ke kon inhein pehley likhey (aur Allah Taala key huzur pesh kerey)."
1064,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Imam (Samiallahu liman hamida) kahe to tum (ربنا ولک الحمد) kaho kyonkey jis aadmi ka ye qol farishton key qol key sath mil gaya, uskey pehley sab gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
1065,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya aur hamarey liye tareeqaey zindagi bayan farmaya aur hamein namaz sikhlaai, chunanche aap ney farmaya : jab tum namaz padho to apni saffen sidhi karo. phir tum mein sey eik shakhs jamaat karwaaey. phir jab Imam (Allahu-Akbar) kahe to tum bhi takbir kaho aur jab woh (غیر المغضوب علیھم wala الضالین) kahe to tum Aameen kaho. Allah Taala (tumhari dua) qubul farmaeyga. aur jab wo Allahu-Akbar keh kar rukoo karey to tum bhi Allahu-Akbar keh kar rukoo karo. Imam tum sey pehley rukoo ko jata hai aur pehley sar uthata hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to wo sabqat is takheer key badley mein hai. aur jab wo (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kahey to tum (اللھم ! ربنا ولک الحمد) kaho. Allah Taala tumhari (hamd ko) zarur suneyga kyonkey Allah Taala ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani farmaya hai ke Allah Taala har us bandey ki baat sunta hai jo uski hamd karta hai. phir jab wo (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sajda karey to tum bhi (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sajda karo kyonkey Imam tum sey pehley sajdey ko jata hai aur pehley sar uthata hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to ye takheer is sabqat key badley mein hai. aur jab wo tashahud key liye bethey to tum mein sey har shakhs ki pehli baat ye honi chahiye : (التحیات الطیبات الصلوات للہ ، سلام علیک ایھا النبی ! و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ ، سلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہ),''tamam achchhey aadaab aur tamam ibaadaten sirf Allah key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ki salamti, rahmatein aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah key tamam nek bandon par bhi Allah ki salamti ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi sachcha mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain.'' yeh saat jumley hain aur ye namaz key salam aur aadaab hain."
1066,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka rukoo, rukoo sey sar uthaney key baad qauma, aap ka sajda aur do sajdon key darmiyan bethna taqriban barabar hota tha."
1067,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab (rukoo sey uthtey waqt) (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kehtey to yun farmatey : (اللھم ! ربنا لک الحمد … … … من شیی بعد),''aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! terey hi liye tareef hai, is qadr ke aasman aur zamin bhar jaeyn aur har wo chiz bhar jaey jo to unkey baad chahey."
1068,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu Anhuma sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo key baad sajda karney ka irada farmatey to yun kehtey : (اللھم ! ربنا لک الحمد … … … من شیی بعد),''aey Allah ! aey hamarey paalney waley ! terey hi liye hai sab tareef jo aasmano aur zamin ko bharney key barabar ho aur har us chiz ko bharney key barabar ho jo to inkey baad chahey."
1069,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ( Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kehtey to yun farmatey : ( ربنا لک الحمد … … … منک الجد ),''aey hamarey Rab ! terey hi liye tareef hai aasmano aur zaminon key bharney key ba-qadr aur har us chiz key bharney key ba-qadr jo to inkey baad chahey. aey buzurgi aur sanaa key laaiq ! behtareen baat jo kisi bandey ney kahi, aur hum sab terey bandey hain, ye hai ke jo chiz to deney ka faisla kar ley koi usey rokney wala nahin aur kisi maal waley ko us ka maal terey nazdik nafa nahin dey sakta.''"
1070,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi. jab aap ney namaz shuru farmaee to mainey aap ko kehtey suna : (اللہ اکبر ذاالحبروت و الملکوت والکبریاء و العظمۃ),''Allah sab sey bada hai, aey azimushshan ghalbey aur badshahi waley ! (be-inteha) buzurgi (badai) aur azmat key Malik ! . aur aap apney rukoo mein farmatey they : (Subhan Rabbiyal Azeem) pak hai mera azmat wala Rab. aur jab aap ney rukoo sey sar uthaya to farmaya : (لربی الحمد لربی الحمد),''merey Rab hi key liye hai sab tareef. merey Rab hi key liye hai sab tareef.'' aur apney sajdey mein farmatey : (Subhan Rabbiyal-aala), ''paak hai mera buzurg aur bartar Rab.'' aur do sajdon key darmiyan farmatey : (رب اغفرلی رب اغفرلی),''aey merey Rab ! mujhey maaf farma, aey merey rab ! mujhey maaf farma."" aur aap ka qiyam, rukoo,  rukoo sey sar uthaney key baad qauma, sajda aur do sajdon key darmiyan waqfa (jalsa yaani thodi der baithna) taqriban barabar they."
1071,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik mahina rukoo key baad qunoot farmaey. aap Real, Zakwaan aur Usba qabaayel par bad'duaa kartey they. (kyonkey) unhoney Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki ma'siyat (nafarmani) ki thi."
1072,Hazrat ibne Sirin sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney subah ki namaz mein qunoot padhi hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. puchha gaya : rukoo sey pehley ya baad? aap ney farmaya : rukoo key baad.
1073,Hazrat ibne Sirin bayan kartey hain ke mujhey eik aisey sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namazey-subah padhi. (unkey bayan key mutabiq) jab aap ney dusri rakat mein (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kaha to aap kuchh der khadey rahey.
1074,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab subah ki namaz ki dusri rakat key rukoo sey sar uthatey to farmatey : aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed, Salma bin Hisham, Ayaash bin Abu-Rabeea aur Makka mein dusrey kamzor aur mazloom musalmanon ko najat dey. aey Allah ! Muzir (Quraish) par apna azab sakht farma aur us azab ko qehat ki surat mein nazil farma jo Yusuf alehissalam key daur key qehat ki tarah ho."
1075,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz mein jab (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) (ربنا ولک الحمد ) padhtey to sajdey mein janey sey pehley khadey khadey dua farmatey : ( اللھم ! انج الولید … … … الخ ), ''aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed, Salma bin Hisham, Ayaash bin Abu-Rabeea aur dusrey kamzor musalmanon ko najat ata farma. aey Allah ! Muzir (Quraish) par apna azab sakht farma aur usey Yusuf alehissalam key daur key qehat ki surat mein nazil farma.'' phir aap (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey aur sajdey ko jatey. un dino Muzir key dehaati qabileyn Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mukhalif they."
1076,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain main tumhein zarur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz samjhaunga to Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Zohar, Isha aur subah ki namazon ki aakhiri rakat mein (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kehney key baad qunoot padhtey jis mein eman walon key liye duaeyn kartey aur kafiron ko lanat kartey they."
1077,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah aur Maghrib ki namaz mein qunoot padha kartey they.
1078,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik mahina rukoo key baad qunoot farmaee. aap chand logon key naam ley kar un par lanat kartey they aur Arab key kuchh qabaayel ka naam ley kar badduaa kartey they. phir aap ney qunoot karna tarak kar di. eik riwayat mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik mahiney tak qunoot farmaee. aap Real, Zakwaan aur Lahyaan (naami qabaayel) par lanat kartey they."
1079,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu Anhuma sey marwi hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap ney jab subah ki namaz mein aakhiri rakat key rukoo sey sar uthaya to farmaya : (اللھم ! العن فلانا و فلانا),''aey Allah ! falan aur falan par lanat farma.''aap munafiq mein sey kuchh logon ka naam ley ley kar badduaa kartey they to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (لیس لک من الامرشیء اویتوب علیھم اویعذبھم فانھم ظلمون),''aap key liye is mamley mein koi ikhtiyar nahin. (ye Allah Taala ka kaam hai ke) wo unhein tauba ki tofiq dey ya unhein azab dey. bilashuba wo zalim hain.''"
1080,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik maah qunoot farmaee. aap Arab key qabaayel mein sey eik qabiley key khilaf badduaa kartey they. phir aap ney qunoot chhod di.
1081,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ashjai ney apney walid mohtaram (Taariq bin Asheem) (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey namaz padhi, aap ney qunoot na farmaee. mainey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi, unhoney bhi qunoot na ki. mainey umr (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi, unhoney bhi qunoot na ki. mainey Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi, unhoney bhi qunoot na ki. mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi, aap ney bhi qunoot na ki. phir farmaya : aey betey ! ye bid'at hai."
1082,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu Anhuma sey riwayat hai, farmatey hain : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Zohar ki namaz padha kartey they to main apni mutthi mein kuchh kankariyaan pakad leta tha taake unhein thanda karun. phir (jab haath jalney lagta to) unhein dusri hatheli mein muntaqil kar leta tha. phir jab main sajda karta to unhein apney maathe key nichey rakh leta."
1083,"Hazrat Mutrif sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney aur mainey Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi. aap jab sajda kartey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey aur jab sajdey sey sar uthatey, tab bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey aur jab do rakaaton sey uthtey, tab bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. jab aap ney namaz puri kar li to Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney mera haath pakda aur farmaya : Allah ki qism ! in sahab ney mujhey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz yad kara di hai."
1084,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har jhukney aur uthney key waqt (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey they aur aakhir mein daeyn baain dono taraf salam phertey they. Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi aisey hi kiya kartey they.
1085,Hazrat Hakim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath ehad kiya tha ke main sajdey mein nahin jaunga magar sidha khada ho kar.
1086,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap apni namaz mein jab rukoo kartey ya rukoo sey sar uthatey ya sajdey mein jatey ya sajdey sey sar uthatey to apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhein kanon key kinaron key barabar kartey."
1087,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney apney dono haath uthaey (rafaul-yadein kiya). phir usi sabiqa (riwayat) ki misl (tarah) bayan kiya."
1088,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap jab namaz shuru farmatey. phir usi (sabiqa hadees) ki tarah bayan kiya. is mein itna ziyada kiya, aur jab rukoo kartey, tab bhi aisey hi kartey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey, phir bhi aisey hi kartey aur jab sajdey sey sar uthatey, tab bhi aisey hi kartey."
1089,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru farmatey jab rukoo kartey aur jab rukoo sey uthtey to rafaul-yadein kartey. lekin sajdey mein (jatey ya sajdey sey uthtey waqt) aisa nahin kartey they.
1090,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha jab aap sajda kartey to apney ghutney,  apney haathon sey pehley rakhtey. aur jab uthtey to apney haath ghutnon sey pehley uthatey."
1091,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (kya) tum mein sey eik aadmi namaz mein bethna chahta hai, phir wo oont ki tarah bethta hai?"
1092,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi aadmi sajda karney lagey to apney haath apney ghutnon sey pehley zamin par rakhey aur oont ki tarah na bethey."
1093,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai aur unhoney isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub kiya hai ke aap ney farmaya : tehqiq dono haath chehrey ki tarah sajda kartey hain. jab tum mein sey koi shakhs apna chehra zamin par rakhey to apney dono haath bhi rakhey aur jab chehra uthaey to inhein bhi utha ley.
1094,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya ke saat aa'zaa (ango) par sajda karen aur namaz key doran mein apney baalon aur kapdon ko ikhatta na karen."
1095,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jab insan sajda karta hai to uskey sath saat aa'zaa (ang) sajda kartey hain is ka chehra, uski do hatheliyan, uskey do ghutney aur uskey do paaun."
1096,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, farmaya : (ramzanul-mubarak ki) ikkeeswin raat ki subah ko meri aakhon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key maathe aur naak par pani aur mitti, yani keechad key nishaanaat dekhey. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
1097,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main saat aa'zaa (ango) par sajda karun aur main baal aur kapdey na sametun. (saat aa'zaa (ang) ye hain) maathaa aur naak, do haath, do ghutney aur do qadam."
1098,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main saat aa'zaa (ango) par sajda karun : maathe par aur (ye kehtey huye) aap ney apni naak ki taraf ishara kiya, dono haathon par, dono ghutnon par aur dono paaun key atraaf par."
1099,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya ke aap saat aa'zaa (ango) par sajda karen … … … aur aap ko baal aur kapdey sametney sey roka gaya … … … dono haathon par, dono ghutnon par aur dono paaun ki ungliyon key kinaron par. (hadees key raawi) Sufiyan ney kaha : ibne Taaus ney apney dono haath apni peshani par rakhey aur unhein naak par sey guzaaraa aur farmaya : ye eik uzu hai. (Imam Nasai ney farmaya) ye (Imam Nasai ney farmaya) lafz (merey Ustad) Muhammad bin Mansoor key hain."
1100,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab banda sajda karta hai to uskey sath saat aa'zaa (ang) sajda kartey hain is ka chehra, uskey dono haath (hatheliyan) uskey dono ghutney aur uskey dono qadam."
1101,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bistar par na paya. (mainey tatolna shuru kiya) mera haath aap ko laga to aap sajdey mein they aur aap key dono paaun khadey they aur aap padh rahey they : (اللھم ! انی اعوذ برضاک … … … کما اثنیت Ali (Raziallahu anhu) نفسک),''aey Allah ! main terey ghussey sey (bachney key liye) teri raza mandi ki panah mein aata hun aur teri saza sey (bachney key liye) teri maafi ki panah mein aata hun aur tujh (terey azab) sey (bachney key liye) teri (rehmat ki) panah mein aata hun. main teri puri tareef nahin kar sakta. to isi tarah hai jis tarah tu ney khud apni tareef ki hai.''"
1102,Hazrat Abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey huye zamin par girtey to apney bazu baghlon sey door rakhtey aur apney paaun ki ungliyon ko (qibley ki taraf ) mod letey. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
1103,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Madina Munawra aaya to mainey (apney dil mein) kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ko ba-ghaur dekhunga. (mainey dekha ke ) aap ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur apney haath uthaey yahan tak ke mainey aap key angoothey aap key kanon key qarib dekhey. jab aap ney rukoo karney ka irada kiya to (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur apney dono haath uthaey, phir apna sar (rukoo sey) uthaya to aap ney kaha : (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) phir (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur sajda kiya to aap key dono haath kanon sey usi jagah they jahan namaz shuru kartey waqt they (yani kanon key barabar they)."
1104,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi aadmi sajdey ki haalat mein apney bazu is tarah zamin par na phelaey jis tarah kutta phelata hai."
1105,"Hazrat Abu-Is'haaq ney kaha ke Hazrat Bara bin Aazib ney hamein sajda karney ka tariqa bayan kiya to apney dono haath zamin par rakhey, sareen (peeth) ko ooncha kiya aur farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah (sajda) kartey dekha hai."
1106,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz mein sajda kartey to apney dono bazu kholtey, inhein apney pehluon sey door rakhtey aur pet ko zamin sey ooncha rakhtey."
1107,Hazrat Abdullah bin Malik ibne Baheena (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz mein sajda farmatey to apney bazu kholtey yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aati.
1108,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke agar main (muqtadi honey ki bajaey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney hota to main (aap key sajda farmaney key waqt) aap ki baghlein dekh leta. Abu-Mujliz (raawi) ney kaha : malum hota hai, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt namaz mein they, is liye yun farmaya."
1109,Hazrat Abdullah bin Aqram (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namazein padhein jab aap sajda farmatey to main aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhta tha.
1110,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda farmatey to apney dono haathon ko itna kushada rakhtey ke agar bhaid bakri ka chhota sa bachcha aap key bazuon key nichey sey guzarnaa chahta to guzar sakta tha.
1111,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sajdey mein aetidaal (beech ka raasta) ikhtiyar karo aur koi shakhs apney bazu is tarah zamin par na bichhaaey jis tarah kutta bichhaataa hai. ye lafz Hazrat Is-haq bin Ibrahim key hain."
1112,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo namaz durust nahin hoti jis mein namazi rukoo aur sajdey key doran mein apni kamar ko sidha na kerey."
1113,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Shabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen chizon sey mana farmaya : kowey ki tarah thongein maarney sey, darindey ki tarah bazu bichaney sey aur aadmi namaz key liye eik hi jagah muqarrar kar ley, jaisey oont (bethney key liye) eik jagah muqarrar kar leta hai."
1114,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main saat aa'zaa (ango) par sajda karun aur (sajdey mein jatey waqt) baal aur kapdey na sametun."
1115,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney Abdullah bin Haris ko namaz padhtey dekha jab ke wo sar key baalon ka juda bana kar usey peechey baandhey huye they. aap uthey aur baalon ka juda (guchchaa) kholney lagey. Abdullah bin Haris namaz sey farigh huye to ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar kehney lagey : aap ko merey baalon sey kiya shikayat thi? (jo aap ney inhein khola) unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna : is qisam key namazi ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jo peechhey bandhey huye haathon sey namaz padhta hai.
1116,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya ke saat aa'zaa (ango) par sajda karen aur mana kiya gaya baal ya kapdey ikhattey karney (sametney) sey.
1117,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jab hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey dophare key waqt sakht garmi mein namaz padhtey to garmi sey bachney key liye apney kapdon par sajda kar liya kartey they.
1118,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rukoo aur sajda mukammal karo. Allah ki qism ! main tumhein apney peechhey tumharey rukoo aur sajdey mein dekhta hun."
1119,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey merey Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen chizon sey mana farmaya hai, main ye nahin kehta ke sab logon ko mana farmaya hai, soney ki anguthi pehan'ney sey, qassi aur za'fraani zard rang ka kapda pehan'ney sey aur sajdey ya rukoo ki haalat mein Quran Majeed padhney sey."
1120,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney rukoo aur sajdey ki haalat mein Quran Majeed padhney sey roka hai.
1121,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney marze wafat mein ghar ki khidki ka parda hataayaa. aap ka sar mubarak patti sey bandhaa huwa tha. aap ney farmaya : aey Allah ! mainey tera Deen logon tak pahuncha diya (teen dafa farmaya). aey logo ! nabuwat key zariey sey khush-khabri deney wali chizon mein sey sirf nek khuwab hi reh gaey hain jinhein koi shakhs dekh ley ya uskey liye kisi dusrey ko nazar aayen. khabrdar ! mujhey rukoo aur sajdey mein Quran Majeed padhney sey rok diya gaya hai, lihaza jab tum rukoo karo to apney Rab ki azmat bayan karo (tasbeehaat padho) aur jab sajda karo to puri koshish sey dua karo kyonkey sajdey ki dua qubuliyat key bahut laaiq hai."
1122,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke mainey apni khaala Memuna binte Haris Raziallahu anhuma key ghar raat guzari. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi unkey paas wahin aaram farma they. mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap qazaey hajat (peshaab paakhaaney se faargh hon) key liye uthey. phir aap mishkeezey key paas aaye, us ka band khola, phir darmiyana sa wuzu kiya. phir apney bistar par tashrif laye aur sau gaey. phir dobara uthey aur mishkeezey key paas gaey, us ka band khola, phir mukammal wuzu farmaya, phir khadey ho kar namaz padhney lagey. aap apney sajdey mein kehtey they : (اللھم ! اجعل فی dili … … … واعظم لی نورا),''aey Allah ! merey dil ko munawwar farma, merey kaan munawwar farma, meri aankhen roshan kar dey. mujh par ooper nichey sey Noor barsa. merey daeyn baain ko munawwar farma. mujhey aagey peechhey sey purnoor farma aur mujhey azeem Noor ata farma.'' phir (namaz mukammal karney key baad) aap so gaey yahan tak ke khraatey bhadney lagey. kuchh der baad Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur aap ko namaz key liye jagaya."
1123,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo aur sajdey mein ye padha kartey they : ( سبحانک اللھم ! ربنا وبحمدک اللھم ! اغفرلی ), ''aey Allah ! hamarey Rab ! to har qism key aeib aur naqaayis sey paak hai aur tamam khoobiyon ka hamil hai. aey Allah ! mujhey maaf farma.'' aap Quran par amal kartey they."
1124,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo aur sajdey mein ye dua padhtey they : (سبحانک اللھم ! ربنا وبحمدک اللھم ! اغفرلی),''aey Allah ! hamarey Rab ! to har qism key aeib aur naqaayis sey pak hai aur har qism ki khoobiyon aur ta'reefon wala hai. aey Allah ! mujhey maaf farma.'' aap Quran par amal farmatey they."
1125,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : (eik dafa) mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bistar par na paya to main aap ko dhoondney lagi. mainey khayal kiya ke aap apni kisi laundi key paas chaley gaey hongey. (mainey tatolna shuru kiya) to mera haath aap ko laga. aap sajdey ki haalat mein they aur padh rahey they : (اللھم ! اغفرلی ما اسررت وما اعلنت),''aey Allah ! merey gunah maaf farma jo mainey chhup kar kiye aur jo mainey elaniya kiye."
1126,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (eik raat) mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko na paya to mainey samjha ke aap apni kisi biwi ya laundi key paas chaley gaey hongey. mainey aap ko talash karna shuru kar diya to aap sajdey mein they, ye dua farma rahey they : aey merey Rab ! mujhey maaf farma dey, wo gunah jo mainey chhup kar kiye aur jo mainey elaniya kiye."
1127,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey to farmatey : (اللھم ! لک سجدت … … … احسن الخالقین), ''aey Allah ! mainey terey hi liye sajda kiya aur terey hi liye muteea huwa aur tujhi par eman laya, merey chehrey ney us zaat key liye sajda kiya jisney isey paida kiya, is ki surat banai aur achchhi surat banai aur is mein kaan aur aankhen banaeen. ba-barkat hai Allah jo sab sey behtar paida karney wala hai."
1128,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney sajdey mein ye padhtey they : (اللھم ! لک سجدت … … … احسن الخالقین),''aey Allah ! mainey terey hi liye sajda kiya aur tujhi par eman laya aur terey hi liye muteea huwa. to mera Rab hai. merey chehrey ney us zaat key liye sajda kya jisney isey paida kiya aur is ki surat banai aur is mein kaan aur aankhen banaeen. ba-barkat hai Allah Taala jo sab sey behtar paida karney wala hai."
1129,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to nafl padhtey jab sajda kartey to kehtey : (اللھم ! لک سجدت … … … احسن الخالقین),''aey Allah ! mainey terey hi liye sajda kiya, tujhi par eman laya, apney aap ko terey supurd kiya. aey Allah ! to mera Rab hai. merey chehrey ney us zaat key liye sajda kya jisney isey paida kiya aur is ki surat banai aur is mein aankh aur kaan banaey. ba-barkat hai Allah sab sey behtar paida karney wala."
1130,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ki namaz mein sajda tilawat key doran mein ye dua padhtey they : (سجد وجھی للذی خلقہ ... ... وقوتہ), ''merey chehrey ney us zaat key liye sajda kiya jisney usey paida kiya aur apni tadbeer aur quwat sey is mein aankh aur kaan paida kiye."
1131,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : eik raat mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (bistar par) na paya. (talash kiya) to aap sajdey ki haalat mein miley aur aap ki ungliyan qibley ki taraf mudi hui thin. mainey suna, aap farma rahey they : (اعوذ برضاک من سخطک … … … Ali (Raziallahu anhu) نفسک),''(aey Allah ! ) main terey ghussey sey (bachney key liye) teri raza mandi ki panah mein aata hun. aur teri saza sey (bachney key liye) teri maafi ki panah mein aata hun. aur tujh sey (terey azab sey bachney key liye) teri panah mein aata hun. main teri puri tareef nahin kar sakta. to isi tarah hai jis tarah tu ney khud apni tareef ki hai.''"
1132,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : eik raat mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (bistar par) na paya to mainey socha aap apni kisi dusri biwi key paas gaey hongey. mainey aap ko tatolna shuru kiya to aap rukoo ya sajdey ki haalat mein they aur padh rahey they : (سبحانک اللھم ! و بحمدک لا الہ الا انت),''aey Allah ! Tu Pak hai aur ta'reefon wala hai. terey siwa koi sachcha mabood nahin.''mainey kaha : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! main kis khayal mein thi aur aap kis shaan mein hain?"
1133,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz key liye utha. aap ney sab sey pehley miswak farmaee aur wuzu kiya. phir khadey ho kar namaz shuru farmaee. (Soora Fatiha key baad) aap ney Sura Baqra shuru ki. aap jab bhi koi rehmat wali aayat padhtey to rukte aur rehmat ka sawal farmatey aur azab ki aayat padhtey to rukte aur azab sey panah maangtey. phir aap ney rukoo farmaya aur apney qiyam key barabar rukoo mein thehrey. aap rukoo mein ye dua padhtey : (سبحان ذی الجبروت و الملکوت والکبریاء و العظمۃ), ''pak hai azeem quwat, badshahi, buzurgi wala aur azmat ka Malik.'' phir aap ney rukoo key barabar sajda farmaya aur apney sajdey mein bhi yehi padhtey rahey : pak hai azimushshan quwat, be-misal badshahi, be-inteha buzurgi aur azmat ka Malik. phir dusri rakat mein aap ney Aale-Imran padhi. phir eik aur surat, phir eik aur sura aur is (rakat) mein bhi aap ney (rukoo aur sujood) aisey hi kiye."
1134,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi. aap ney (Soora Fatiha key baad) Sura Baqra shuru ki. aap ney sau aayaat padh lein magar rukoo na farmaya balke qirat jari rakhi. mainey socha : aap do rakaat mein puri kar leingey magar aap ney qirat jari rakhi. mainey (dil mein) kaha : ye sura khatam kar key rukoo farmaeyngey magar aap padhtey rahey yahan tak ke Sura Nisa bhi padh dali. phir Sura Aale Imran padhi, phir taqriban apney qiyam key barabar rukoo farmaya. apney rukoo mein kehtey rahey : (Subhan Rabbiyal Azeem, Subhan Rabbiyal Azeem, Subhan Rabbiyal Azeem) par sar uthaya aur farmaya : (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) (ربنا لک الحمد ) aur bahut der tak khadey  (kuchh padhtey) rahey. phir sajda farmaya aur bahut lamba sajda farmaya. aur sajdey mein padhtey rahey : (Subhan Rabbiyal-aala, Subhan Rabbiyal-aala, Subhan Rabbiyal-aala) aap junhi koi daraney wali ya Allah Taala ki azmat wali aayat padhtey to (us key munasib) dua aur Allah Taala ka zikr farmatey."
1135,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo aur sajdey mein ye tasbih padhtey they : (سبوح قدوس رب الملائکۃ والروح),''bahut pak hai, paak hai farishton aur Roohe-pak (Jibril Ameen) ka Rab."
1136,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey kisi ko us jawan, yani Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez sey badh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key mushabeh (jaisi) namaz padhtey nahin dekha. hamney rukoo aur sajdey mein un ki tasbeehaat ka andaza das tasbeehaat ka lagaya."
1137,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, farmatey hain : eik baar aisa huwa ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (masjid mein) bethey they aur hum aap key ird-gird (halqa baandhey huye) they. itney main eik aadmi aaya aur wo masjid ki qibley wali deewar key paas ja kar namaz padhney laga. jab us ney namaz mukammal kar li to wo aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aur sab logon ko salam kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : ja phir namaz padh kyonkey tu ney namaz nahin padhi. wo gaya aur phir namaz padhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uski namaz ko ba-ghaur dekhtey rahey. usey ilm nahin tha ke aap uski kon si ghalati pakad rahey hain. jab wo namaz padh chuka to phir aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aur sab logon ko salam kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (وعلیک), ja namaz padh, tu ney namaz nahin padhi. us ney do ya teen dafa namaz padhi. aakhir us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney meri namaz mein kya ghalati mehsus farmaee hai? aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey kisi ki namaz mukammal nahin hoti jab tak wo achchhi tarah wuzu na karey jis tarah ke Allah Taala ney usey hukm diya hai, yani wo apna chehra aur kohniyon tak haath dhoey. apney sar ka masah karey aur takhnon tak paaun dhoey. phir (Allahu-Akbar) kahe aur Allah ki hamd aur buzurgi bayan karey (sanaa padhey). aur jo Quran usey aasan ho, jo usey Allah Taala ney sikhlaya hai aur usey tofiq di hai, padhey. phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar rukoo karey yahan tak ke uskey jod mutmain ho jaeyn aur apni mojud jagah par thehar jaeyn. phir wo (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) keh kar sidha khada ho jaey aur apni pusht ko bilkul apni asli haalat mein kerey. phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sajda karey yahan tak ke apney chehrey ko achchhi tarah zamin par jamaey yahan tak ke uskey jod mutmain aur pursukoon ho jaeyn aur apni apni jagah thehar jaeyn. phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sar uthaey aur maqa'd (sareen/peeth ) par achchhi tarah beth jaey aur apni kamar ko bilkul sidha kar ley. phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sajda karey aur apney chehrey ya maathe ko zamin par jamaey aur tikaaey. jab tak (namaz mein) aisey na karey. uski namaz puri nahin hoti."
1138,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : banda apney Rab key sab sey ziyada qarib sajdey ki haalat mein hota hai, lihaza sajdey mein khub dua kiya karo."
1139,Hazrat Rabeea bin Kaab Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aap key wuzu ka pani aur dusri zarooriyaat mohaiyya kiya karta tha. aap ney farmaya : mujh sey (kuchh) mang. mainey kaha : jannat mein aap ki rafaqat maangta hun. aap ney farmaya : koi aur chiz? mainey kaha : bas yehi maangta hun. aap ney farmaya : is silsiley main to sajdon (nafl namaz) ki kasrat key zariey sey meri madad kar.
1140,"Hazrat Ma'daan bin Talha Yaamari bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila aur guzarish ki : mujhey aisa amal bataiye jo mujhey nafa dey ya mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar dey. aap kuchh der khamosh rahey, phir meri taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : kasrate sujood ko lazim pakad kyonkey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna hai : jo banda Allah Taala key liye sajdey karta hai, Allah Taala us sajdey ki wajeh sey us ka darja buland farmata hai aur eik ghalati maaf farmata hai. Ma'daan ney kaha : phir main Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila aur un sey bhi wohi sawal kiya jo Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey kiya tha. unhoney bhi farmaya : sajdey (kasrat key sath) kiya kar kyonkey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : jo banda khalis Allah Taala key liye sajda karta hai to Allah Taala us sajdey ki bina par us ka darja buland farmata hai aur uski ghalati (ya ghaltiyaan) maaf farmata hai."
1141,"Hazrat Ata bin Yazid bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Raziallahu anhuma key paas betha tha. un mein sey eik ney Shafa'at wali hadees sunai aur doosra khamosh betha tha. us (sahabi) ney farmaya : farishtey aayengey aur sifarish kerengey. tamam Rasool Alaihimussalam bhi sifarish farmaeyngey. phir unhoney pul-siraat ka zikr kar key kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main sab sey pehley guzrunga. phir jab Allah Taala bandon key darmiyan insaf kar key farigh ho jaeyga aur jinhein aag sey nikalna chaheyga, unhein nikalney lageyga to farishton aur Rasulon ko sifarish karney ka hukm deyga to unhein unkey (sajdon key) nishaanaat sey pehchana jaeyga kyonkey aag insan key har uzu ko jala degi magar sajdey wali jagahon ko na jala sakeygi. chunanche (jahannam sey nikal kar) un par aabe hayaat dala jaeyga, to wo aisey (khoobsurat) ugengey jaisey sailaabi kudaa karkat mein dana ugta hai."
1142,"Hazrat Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Maghrib ya Isha ki namaz key liye Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to aap ney Hazrat Hasan ya Husain Raziallahu anhuma ko utha rakha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (namaz padhaaney key liye) aagey badhey aur bachchey ko nichey bitha diya. phir namaz key liye takbire-tahreema kahi aur namaz shuru kar di. namaz key doran mein aap ney eik sajda bahut lamba kar diya. mainey sar utha kar dekha to bachcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki pusht par betha tha aur aap sajdey mein they. main dobara sajdey mein chala gaya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz puri farmaee to logon ney guzarish ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney namaz key doran main eik sajda is qadr lamba kiya ke hamney samjha koi haadisa ho gaya hai ya aap ko ""wahi"" aaney lagi hai. aap ney farmaya : aisa kuchh bhi nahin huwa balke mera beta meri pusht par sawar ho gaya to mainey pasand na kiya ke usey jaldi mein dalun (fauran utaar dun) yahan tak ke wo apna dil khush kar ley."
1143,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap har jhuktey, uthtey, bethtey aur khadey hotey waqt (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey they aur apney daeyn baain (السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ) tum par Allah Taala ki salamti aur rehmat ho. kehtey yahan tak ke aap key rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati thi. aur mainey Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma ko bhi isi tarah kartey dekha."
1144,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru farmatey to apney dono haath uthatey aur jab rukoo kartey to aisey kartey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to aisey kartey aur jab sajdey sey apna sar uthatey to un sab mein aisey hi kartey, yani rafaul-yadein kartey."
1145,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru farmatey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey aur rafaul-yadein kartey. isi tarah jab rukoo mein jatey aur rukoo sey sar uthatey (tab bhi aisa hi kartey). lekin do sajdon key darmiyan rafaul-yadein nahin kartey they."
1146,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunchey (to aap namaz padh rahey they) aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath pehlu mein khadey ho gaey. aap ney farmaya : (اللہ اکبر ذوالملکوت والجبروت والکبریاء والعظمۃ),''Allah sab sey bada hai, wo badshahi, azimushshan quwat, be-inteha buzurgi aur azmat ka Malik hai.''phir aap ney (Soora Fatiha key baad) Sura Baqra tilawat farmaee. phir rukoo farmaya. aap ka rukoo taqriban aap key qiyam key barabar tha. aap ney rukoo mein (bar-bar) padha : (Subhan Rabbiyal Azeem, Subhan Rabbiyal Azeem) aur jab rukoo sey sar uthaya to (Samiallahu-liman-hamida kehney key baad) farmaya : (لربی الحمد , لربی الحمد)' ''merey Rab key liye hi sab tareefen hain, merey Rab key liye hi sab tareefen hain.'' aur aap apney sajdey mein padhtey rahey : (Subhan Rabbiyal-aala, Subhan Rabbiyal-aala) aur aap do sajdon key darmiyan padhtey rahey : (رب اغفرلی رب اغفرلی),''aey merey Rab ! mujhey maaf farma dey, aey merey Rab ! mujhey maaf farma dey.''"
1147,"Abu Sahal Azdi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Taaus ney Meena ki masjid khaif mein merey sath namaz padhi. unhoney jab pehla sajda karney key baad sar uthaya to apney dono haath apney chehrey key samney uthaey. mainey is kaam ko durust na samjha. mainey (apney sathi) Wuhaib bin Khalid sey kaha ke ye aisa kaam kartey hain jo mainey kisi aur ko kartey nahin dekha. Wuhaib ney un sey kaha, aap aisa kaam kartey hain jo mainey kisi aur ko kartey nahin dekha. Abdullah bin Taaus ney kaha : mainey apney walid mohtaram ko aisey kartey dekha hai aur unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko aisey kartey dekha hai aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
1148,Hazrat Memuna Raziallahu anhuma farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey to apney bazuon ko kholtey yahan tak ke peechhey sey baghlon ki safedi nazar aati thi aur jab bethtey they to baain raan par itminan sey bethtey.
1149,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz mein aap ka rukoo aur sajda aur rukoo sey sar uthaney key baad qiyam aur do sajdon key darmiyan jalsa (bethna) taqriban barabar hotey they.
1150,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har uthney, jhukney aur qiyam aur qaaede (khadey honey aur bethney) key waqt (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey they aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhu bhi aisey hi kartey they."
1151,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. phir jab rukoo farmatey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. phir jab rukoo sey apni pusht uthatey to (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kehtey. phir khadey khadey kehtey : (ربنا لک الحمد) phir jab sajdey key liye jhuktey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. phir jab sajdey sey sar uthatey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. phir jab doosra sajda kartey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. phir jab sajdey sey sar uthatey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. phir sari namaz mein aisey hi kartey yahan tak ke usey mukammal farmatey. aur jab do rakaaton key baad beth kar uthtey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey.
1152,"Hazrat Abu-Qulaba sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) hamari masjid mein tashrif laye aur farmaya : main chahta hun, main tumhein dikhaaun ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kaisey namaz padhtey dekha hai. unhoney kaha : aap ney jab pehli rakat mein dusrey sajdey sey sar uthaya to beth gaey."
1153,Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz padhtey dekha. jab aap apni namaz ki taaq rakat mein hotey to aap khadey nahin hotey they yahan tak ke pehley sidhey beth jatey.
1154,"Abu Qulaba sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye they aur kehtey they : kya main tumharey samney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz na bayan karun? phir wo kisi farz namaz key waqt key ilawa (nafl) namaz padhtey jab wo pehli rakat key dusrey sajdey sey sar uthatey to sidhey bethtey, phir khadey hotey aur zamin par haathon ka sahara letey."
1155,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, jab aap sajda kartey to apney dono ghutney apney dono haathon sey pehley rakhtey aur jab uthtey to dono haath ghutnon sey pehley uthatey. Abu-Abdur-Rehmaan (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat Shareek sey Yazid bin Harun key ilawa kisi ney bhi is tarah bayan nahin ki. (Allah ziyada behtar jaanta hai)."
1156,Hazrat Abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hamein namaz padhatey to jab bhi (rukoo aur sajdey key liye) jhuktey aur (sajdey sey) uthtey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey. jab namaz sey farigh hotey to farmatey : Allah ki qism ! yaqinan main apni namaz main tum sab sey badh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mushabeh (tarah) hun.
1157,Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman aur Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhi. unhoney jab rukoo kiya to Allahu-Akbar kaha. jab rukoo sey sar uthaya to (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) (ربنا ولک الحمد) kaha. phir sajdey mein gaey to (Allahu-Akbar) kaha. sajdey sey sar uthaya to (Allahu-Akbar) kaha. phir jab rakat sey uthey to (Allahu-Akbar) kaha. phir farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! main namaz main tum sab sey badh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mushabeh (jaisa) hun aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz yehi rahi yahan tak ke aap duniya sey juda ho gaey (faut ho gaey). ye lafz Hazrat Sawwar key hain.
1158,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain : tehqiq namaz mein ( bethney ka) tariqa ye hai ke to apna baayan paaun bichhaey aur daayan paaun khada kerey.
1159,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain : namaz mein ( bethney ka) tariqa ye hai ke to daeyn paaun ko khada karey aur uski ungliyan qibla rukh karey aur baain paaun par bethey.
1160,Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya to mainey dekha ke aap jab namaz shuru farmatey aur jab rukoo ka irada farmatey to apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhein kandhon key barabar farmatey aur jab do rakaaton key baad bethtey to baain paaun ko bichhatey aur daeyn ko khada kartey aur apna daayan haath apni daeyn raan par rakhtey aur apni (tashahud ki) ungli duaaey tashahud key liye uthatey aur baayan haath baain raan par rakhtey. phir main agley saal aaya to mainey dekha ke sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum apney-apney jubbon mein rafaul-yadein kartey they.
1161,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney eik aadmi ko dekha jo apney haath sey namaz mein kankariyon sey khel raha tha. jab wo farigh huwa to us sey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : namaz mein kankariyon ko na chhua kar, is liye ke ye shetan ki taraf sey hai. lekin is tarah kar jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kya kartey they. us ney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kaisey kya kartey they? Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney apna daayan haath apni daain raan par rakha aur anguthey key sath wali ungli sey qibley ( samney ) ki taraf ishara kya aur apni nazar is par tikaai, phir farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
1162,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab do ya chaar rakaat key baad bethtey to apney haath apney ghutnon par rakhtey. phir ungli sey ishara farmatey they.
1163,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney taalim di ke jab hum do rakaaton key baad bethein to ye padhein : التحیات للہ … … و رسولہ tamam aadab (qauli ibadatein), duayen (ya badani ibadatein) aur achey kaam o kalimat (ya maali ibadatein) Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ki taraf sey salamti, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah key dusrey tamam nek bandon par salamti ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi sacha mabood nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah key bandey aur Rasool hain."
1164,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum (pehley pehal) nahin jantey they ke do rakaton key baad (beth kar) kya padhein magar hum tasbih, takbir aur apney rab ki hamd padhtey rehtey they. Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen neki ki ibtida (shuruat) o inteha (neki key tamam maamlon) ki taalim di. aap ney farmaya : jab tum har do rakaton key baad betho to ye padho : التحیات للہ والصلوات … … … tamam aadaab, duayen aur achey kalimat Allah Taala hi key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ki taraf sey salamti, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key dusrey nek bandon par bhi salamti ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. aur tum mein sey har aadmi wo dua muntakhab karey jo usey ziyada achi lagey. phir Allah Taala sey wo dua kerey."
1165,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz mein (padhney key liye) tashahud aur dusri zaruriyat key liye tashahud sikhaya. namaz wala tashahud to ye hai : التحیات للہ والصلوات … … … tamam qouli ibadatein, badani ibadatein aur maali ibadatein Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ki taraf sey salamti, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi salamti ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain."
1166,"Hazrat Yahya bin Adam bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Sufiyan ko ye tashahud farz aur nafl dono qism ki namaz mein padhtey suna aur wo kehtey they : hamen (ye tashahud ) abu-Is-haq ney Abul-Ahwas sey, unhon (Abul-Ahwas) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan kya."
1167,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath rehtey they. (pehley) hum kuch nahin jantey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen farmaya : har jalsey, yani tashahud mein kaho : التحیات للہ و الصلوات و الطیبات ، السلام علیک ایھا النبی و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ ، السلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہ"
1168,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum nahin jantey they ke namaz padhein to kya kahen. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen jaamey kalimat sikhlaaey aur hum sey farmaya : tum yun kaho : التحیات للہ و الصلوات و الطیبات ، السلام علیک ایھا النبی و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ ، السلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہHazrat Alqama ney kaha : mainey dekha ke Hazrat ibn-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ye kalimaat hamen is tarah sikhatey jaisey Quran sikhatey they. (lafz lafz hifz karwatey they.)
1169,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhtey to hum ( tashahud mein) kehtey : السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) اللہ ، السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) جبریل السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) میکائیل Allah taala par salam ho, Jibril par salam ho, mekael par salam ho to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ye na kaho ke Allah Taala par salam ho, kyonkey Allah Taala to khud salamti ka manba hai balke tum yun kaho : التحیات للہ والصلوات … … … tamam aadab, namazein aur achey kalmaat Allah Taala key liye hain. aey nabi! aap par Allah Taala ki taraf sey salam, rehmat aur barkatein hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key nek bandon par bhi salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi sacha mabood nahin. wo akela hai. uska koi shareek nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain."
1170,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhtey they to kehtey they : السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) اللہ ، السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) جبریل السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) میکائیل Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum (Assalam alallah) na kaho kyonkey Allah Taala to khud salam hai, balke tum kaho : التحیات للہ والصلوات والطیبات ، السلام علیک ایھا النبی و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ السلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہ"
1171,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen tashahud key barey mein batlaya : التحیات للہ والصلوات والطیبات ، السلام علیک ایھا النبی و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ السلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہ abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (us riwayat mein) Abu Hashim ka zikr gharib hai.
1172,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye tashahud is tarah sikhaya jis tarah Quran Majeed ki koi sura sikhatey they. (jab aap ney mujhey ye tashahud sikhaya to) meri hatheli aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key dono mubarak haathon key darmiyan thi : التحیات للہ والصلوات والطیبات ، السلام علیک ایھا النبی و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ السلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہ
1173,"Hazrat ( Abu-Musa ) Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen khutba diya. hamen hamarey tareeqey bataey aur hamari namaz hamarey liye bayan farmaey, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni safein sidhi aur durust karo. phir tum mein sey eik aadmi tumhari imaamat karaaey. jab wo « Allahu-akbar » kahey to tum «Allahu-akbar» kaho aur jab wo «ولا الضالین» kahey to tum Aameen kaho. Allah Taala tum sey qubul farmaeyga. jab wo takbir keh kar rukoo karey to tum bhi takbir keh kar rukoo karo. Imam tum sey pehley rukoo ko jata hai aur pehley sar uthata hai. ye takheer us sabqat key badley mein hai. aur jab wo (Samiallahu liman hamida) kahey to tum ( ربنا ولک الحمد ) kaho. Allah Taala tumhari (hamd) sunega kyonkey Allah Taala ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani irshad farmaya hai ke Allah Taala us shakhs ki baat sunta hai jo uski tareef karta hai. phir jab Imam « Allahu-akbar » keh kar sajda karta hai to tum bhi « Allahu-akbar » keh kar sajda karo. Imam tum sey pehley sajdey ko jata hai aur pehley sar uthata hai. ye takheer us sabqat key badley mein hai. phir jab Imam qaadey mein ho to tum mein sey har aadmi ko sab sey pehley ye kehna chahiye : ( التحیات الطیبات … … … ورسولہ ) tamam pakizah aadaab Allah Taala key liye hain, duayen aur namazein bhi. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ka salam, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi sacha mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain."
1174,"Hazrat Hatan bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke hamney Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) key sath namaz padhi to unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Imam qadey mein ho to tum mein sey har aadmi ki pehli baat ye honi chahiye : التحیات للہ والصلوات والطیبات ، السلام علیک ایھا النبی و رحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ السلام علینا و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) عباد اللہ الصالحین ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ و اشھد ان محمدا عبدہ و رسولہtamam aadaab Allah Taala key liye hain aur tamam achey kalmaat aur duayen bhi Allah key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ka salam, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin. wo akela hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain."
1175,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamen tashahud is tarah sikhatey they jis tarah Quran sikhatey they aur aap farmatey they : ( التحیات المبارکات … … … ورسولہ ) ba-barkat aadab, tamam achey kalimat aur pakizah duayen sab Allah key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salam ho aur Allah Taala ki rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key nek bandon par bhi salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain."
1176,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamen tashahud is tarah sikhatey they jis tarah hamen Quran Majeed ki sura sikhatey they : بسم اللہ و باللہ التحیات … … … من النار Allah key ba-barkat naam aur Allah Taala ki madad aur tofiq key sath tamam aadaab (ya qouli ibadatein), tamam duayen aur namazein (ya badani ibadatein) aur tamam achey kalmaat o kaam (ya maali ibadatein) Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah ki taraf sey salam, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. mein Allah Taala sey jannat maangta hun aur aag sey Allah ki panah chahta hun."
1177,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do rakaaton key baad itna halka bethtey they goya garm pathar par bethey hain. (yani jaldi khadey ho jatey.) Hadees key raawi abu ubaida bayan kartey hain ke mainey puchha : yahan tak ke uth khadey huye. unhoney farmaya : han, yehi murad hai."
1178,"Hazrat Malik ibne-Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik dafa) namaz padhi to do rakaton key baad (bhool kar) khadey ho gaey lekin phir namaz mein jari rahey (wapis na huye) yahan tak ke jab namaz key aakhir mein pahunchey to aap ney salam pherney sey qabl do sajdey (sujood sahw) kiye, phir salam phera."
1179,Hazrat Malik ibne-Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik dafa) namaz padhi to do rakaaton key baad ( bhool kar) khadey ho gaey. logon ney « subhan Allah » kaha magar aap jari rahey ( dobara na bethey ) phir jab namaz sey farigh huye to do sajdey kiye. phir salam phera.
